## 2026-03-28 - Consistency scanner
- Implemented full consistency scanner: scans selection or full page for values close-to-but-not-exactly a design token, surfaces as suggestions with one-click snap-to-token
- **Scanner logic** (`packages/figma-plugin/src/plugin/consistencyScanner.ts`, new): walks nodes, skips already-bound properties, compares fill/stroke colors (RGB Euclidean distance 0.5–10 = "near match"), dimensions (|diff| ≤ 1px), opacity (|diff| ≤ 2%). Groups results by `tokenPath::property` key, sorted by instance count
- **Types** (`packages/figma-plugin/src/shared/types.ts`): added `ScanConsistencyMessage` and added it to `PluginMessage` union

